sql:
select 
    table1."column1", 
    table1."column2", 
    table1."column3", 
    table1."column4" 
from 
    table1 
where 
    table1."column5" = 'value' 
    and (table1."column6" = 'value1' or table1."column7" = 'value2') 
    and table1."column8" >= 'date';
